about.title: About
about.description: I am a software engineer and full stack developer with a passion for thoughtful designs and clean code. With an enthusiasm for the details and a love for making things, I know how to make technology look good and how to make it work efficiently. I am a recent graduate from the University of California, Irvine with a Bachelor's of Science degree in Computer Science.
